  "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_grimstroke_spirit_walk": "Ink Swell",
  "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_grimstroke_spirit_walk_Description": "Grimstroke shrouds an allied unit in ink, increasing its movement speed while silencing and disarming it, as well as making it immune to attacks. Enemies in range of the allied unit are damaged with inky tendrils over time. After %buff_duration% seconds it triggers, applying damage and stun in an area around the unit in proportion to how much ink tendril damage was inflicted across the duration.",
